list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: Added DataFetcher class, which retrieves the raw html text for each given url. In order to use DataFetcher, extend it in your Fragment class and override the onPostExecute(ArrayList<String> rawJsons) method.

task.summary: Added DataFetcher class, which retrieves the raw html text for each given url. In order to use DataFetcher, extend it in your Fragment class and override the onPostExecute(ArrayList<String> rawJsons) method.

Updated DataFetcher class to include a WeakReference to the context in which it runs to avoid making overriding the postExecute method cumbersome, and added a new constructor as such.
Also updated the InvoicesFetcher nested class in InvoicesFragment to reflect the newly added attribute.
Added try/catch blocks for catching NullPointerExceptions when iterating over a possibly empty json string list (possibly due to a bad URL or malformed site data).
